<HEAD>THE COMEDY OF ERRORS.</HEAD>
<DIV3 TYPE="dramatis personae">
<PB REF="152">
<HEAD>Dramatis Per&s;onae.</HEAD>
<LIST>
<HEAD>MEN.</HEAD>
<ITEM>ANTIPHOLIS.</ITEM>
<ITEM>BALTHAZAR.</ITEM>
</LIST>
<LIST>
<HEAD>WOMEN.</HEAD>
<ITEM>An Abbe&s;s.</ITEM>
