<ITEM>LORD STANLEY.</ITEM>
<ITEM>LORD HASTINGS.</ITEM>
<ITEM>BISHOP OF ELY.</ITEM>
<ITEM>BRACKENBURY, Lieutenant of the Tower.</ITEM>
